oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Indian Summer Sky
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (navy and red on white) announcing Indian Summer Sky featuring Fleming and John, Watermelon Road, Cumberland Rose, The Shakers, For Kate's Sake, Chris Miner, Garth Rider, Nina Adel, Sara Majors, The Barbie Syndrome, 4 Zoas, Cereal Killer, The Toby Show, and Randy Mack at Blue Sky Court in Nashville, Tennessee on October 1-4. Poster features a woodcut of a circus scene.
